data.description: Start 2024 off right! This fabulous home has a backyard oasis your whole family is sure to enjoy, and Marine Creek Ranch has a host of amenities including community lake access, a pool, and expansive trails and green areas!!! This home has 4 bedrooms plus a study with closet and 2 living areas with a gorgeous fireplace. The eat-in kitchen boasts a gas cooktop with stainless steel appliances, knotty alder cabinets and granite countertops. Enjoy entertaining and holiday meals in the oversized dining room with butler’s pantry. The generous primary retreat has tons of windows with beautiful light - walk through the hand-crafted farmhouse door and enjoy the spa-like experience of a jetted tub. You will not want to miss this home in EMS-ISD.  Seller Concessions available towards closing costs, upgrades or rate buy-down with acceptable offer.  BUYER HAS ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 4.5%.
